{"tid":730801,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2018韓國小姐出爐 23歲金秀敏奪冠被讚天然美女","createTime":"2018-07-05T16:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T19:21:14.000Z","uid":29627,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e30f9c2582d3d81f480f3f99ddaf96f047e1062c","tid":730801,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:37:01.000Z","msg":"2018韓國小姐出爐 23歲金秀敏奪冠被讚天然美女<br />\n<br />\n今屆2018韓國小姐決賽噚晚於首爾奧林匹克公園舉行，共選出一名「真」（冠軍）、兩名「善」（亞軍）及四名「美」（季軍），當中由嚟自京畿道嘅23歲金秀敏脫穎而出，奪得冠軍，並獲得1億韓圜（約70萬港元）獎金。<br />\n<br />\n現年23歲嘅金秀敏身高1.73米，體重130磅，目前於美國讀大學，志願係當一名記者，興趣係唱歌及跳舞，擅長外語及模仿別人嘅聲音。<br />\n<br />\n金秀敏當選後表示：「難以置信，今後我會一直提醒自己唔可以自滿，一直保持初心，努力去做每一件事。」<br />\n<br />\n以往每屆韓國小姐選舉進行前，網民都會表示入圍佳麗離奇撞樣，搞到網民根本分唔清邊個打邊個，不過今屆韓國小姐似乎撞樣次數少咗，更有網民留言大讚今屆韓國小姐「金秀敏個樣最自然」、「唔係整過容嘅美女」等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180705/large/1530762762_5fcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F1530762762_5fcb.jpg&h=e5494f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n23歲金秀敏奪得2018韓國小姐冠軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180705/large/1530762766_b4e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F1530762766_b4e4.jpg&h=29c738f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身高1.73米嘅金秀敏，獲網民大讚係天然美女。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180705/58402124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58402124&d=uOklBcEPVMBt4WtBUitnIARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=c0ef736f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58402124&h=76bfa7db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180705/58402124</a>"},{"pid":"7bee8fb7fd9512d30038520c617f73b4a27af615","tid":730801,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img2.utuku.china.com/640x0/ent/20180705/ceaf1804-f788-4c52-be3b-207197ccee72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.utuku.china.com%2F640x0%2Fent%2F20180705%2Fceaf1804-f788-4c52-be3b-207197ccee72.jpg&h=838a2d33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是撚旦啦<br />\n邊個贏都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c3d672621b308936eff6283bca489f69ab9c18","tid":730801,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"真係幾正"},{"pid":"6ae29a2ba747195c4f6ca2db2c0efb9606109798","tid":730801,"uid":151664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:19:57.000Z","msg":"個冠軍係幾多號？？認唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1926238bef7a8a5af9426e8a96d6900b1619aec","tid":730801,"uid":14208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ae29a2ba747195c4f6ca2db2c0efb9606109798","tid":730801,"uid":151664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:19:57.000Z","msg":"個冠軍係幾多號？？認唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:45:22.000Z","msg":"14號"},{"pid":"fe5ae45f9846eabddd11329414a8b86a8c0ddbd0","tid":730801,"uid":184932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T18:29:13.000Z","msg":"整容公司 選舉咪算lor"},{"pid":"edffba737d220d401b0c1847af99f5bd0fc3c3e4","tid":730801,"uid":167219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T18:41:41.000Z","msg":"粗粗地望有少少似雪炫"},{"pid":"878df0846587fdb34405336f430fb61a3f84fc4a","tid":730801,"uid":105838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T18:42:45.000Z","msg":"個鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab2bf17937fae5516421c83e7fbe3a92485a071","tid":730801,"uid":38102,"like":2,"di